{"consensus_set_id":"s331703","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"331703"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"<quranic_text> « اِنَّمٰا اَنْتَ مُنْذِرٌ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الرعد ۷ ] </footnote>  ثُمَّ يَرُدُّ يَدَهُ اِلَي صَدْرِهِ - ثُمَّ يَقُولُ :   <quranic_text> « وَ لِكُلِّ قَوْمٍ هٰادٍ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الرعد ۷ ] </footnote>","translation_segment":"عن أبی برزه قال: سمعت رسول الله صلی الله علیه و آله و سلم یقول: (إنما أنت منذر) ثم یرد یده إلی صدره ثم یقول: (و لکل قوم هاد) و یشیر إلی علی‌ بیده. ابو برزه گفت: از پیامبر خدا شنیدم که می‌گوید: «انما انت منذر» و دست خود را به سینه‌اش می‌برد، سپس","segment_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"انما","display":"اِنَّمٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"انت","display":"اَنْتَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"منذر","display":"مُنْذِرٌ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الرعد","display":"الرعد"},{"kind":"word","token":"۷","display":"۷"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"ثم","display":"ثُمَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يرد","display":"يَرُدُّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يده","display":"يَدَهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الي","display":"اِلَي"},{"kind":"word","token":"صدره","display":"صَدْرِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"-","display":"-"},{"kind":"word","token":"ثم","display":"ثُمَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يقول","display":"يَقُولُ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لكل","display":"لِكُلِّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوم","display":"قَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هاد","display":"هٰادٍ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الرعد","display":"الرعد"},{"kind":"word","token":"۷","display":"۷"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"}]},{"source_hadith_segment":"وَ يُشِيرُ اِلَي عَلِيٍّ بِيَد